say that when
he wrote this:

04:12.167 --> 04:15.033
"Frankly, I'm sick
of you. You disgust me.

04:16.767 --> 04:21.733
"I had a full head
of hair when
I met you...

04:21.733 --> 04:26.467
and I'm sure my nose grew
during our marriage."

04:26.467 --> 04:30.534
He says he's going
to Yosemite to be
a park ranger.

04:30.534 --> 04:32.501
He's rejected
materialism

04:32.501 --> 04:36.200
and all the evils
brought about
by the quest for money.

04:36.200 --> 04:38.400
Oh. And he's suing me
for alimony.

04:38.400 --> 04:40.567
[LAUGHING]

04:43.601 --> 04:46.100
Be strong, Marce.
You don't need a man.

04:46.100 --> 04:48.267
I mean, what are they
good for?

04:48.267 --> 04:49.667
They sit there
like a lump.

04:49.667 --> 04:52.567
They pick, they burp,
they let one fly.

04:57.534 --> 05:00.868
And then they smile
like they just won
the Nobel prize.

05:04.167 --> 05:05.200
Oh.

05:08.267 --> 05:10.467
And then once a month,
they roll over on you

05:10.467 --> 05:11.734
on their way
to the bathroom,

05:11.734 --> 05:13.934
and they call that
loving.

05:15.667 --> 05:18.434
Not that you're
not the best, baby.

05:22.367 --> 05:24.767
You should feel lucky
Steve left you.

05:24.767 --> 05:27.334
This is the dawn
of a new age
for you, Marce.

05:27.334 --> 05:30.501
You know, Peggy.
You're right.

05:30.501 --> 05:32.534
I can do better
than Steve.

05:32.534 --> 05:33.834
I have my health.

05:35.067 --> 05:37.167
