Right.

05:37.167 --> 05:39.167
I have my youth.

05:39.167 --> 05:40.667
Right.
Yup.

05:40.667 --> 05:42.300
I've got
my looks.

05:45.033 --> 05:47.934
Thank God I have you
for a support group.

05:47.934 --> 05:49.968
Well, it's Steve's loss.

05:49.968 --> 05:52.868
If he can't handle a strong,
intelligent woman,

05:52.868 --> 05:54.467
then tough noogies on him.

05:55.501 --> 05:56.534
That's right,
Marce.

05:56.534 --> 05:57.968
He'll come crawling
back to you.

05:57.968 --> 05:59.868
He will. I think this
is just gonna blow over.

05:59.868 --> 06:00.868
You'll be just fine.

06:00.868 --> 06:02.234
Go ahead.
Go home.

06:02.234 --> 06:03.367
Right.

06:04.634 --> 06:06.133
I'm gonna go home...

06:06.133 --> 06:08.267
and cut the crotches
out of all of his pants.

06:10.901 --> 06:12.834
And drag his ties
through dog poo.

06:14.701 --> 06:18.033
