No.

06:42.334 --> 06:43.667
I won't be
in the way?

06:43.667 --> 06:45.801
Oh,
of course not.
[MOUTHING WORDS]

06:46.801 --> 06:47.968
Oh, you're
good people...

06:50.000 --> 06:51.200
and good friends.

06:53.300 --> 06:55.501
Marcie, you're more
like family.

06:55.501 --> 06:59.434
Al...brush the fleas
off Buck's blanket.

06:59.434 --> 07:00.868
