how she looks at you.

08:14.734 --> 08:16.467
Well, sure.

08:19.400 --> 08:20.467
How?

08:21.767 --> 08:24.801
Bud, don't be a cowpie
your whole life.

08:24.801 --> 08:26.400
She's hot for you.

08:26.400 --> 08:28.033
She's reaching
her sexual peak.

08:28.033 --> 08:31.334
You're reaching your sexual
peak, sad as that may be.

08:32.501 --> 08:34.100
I mean, this could be
your big chance.

08:34.100 --> 08:35.801
And what woman
wouldn't want a virgin?

08:35.801 --> 08:36.801
Yeah!

08:41.234 --> 08:44.033
I'll-- I'll lie to her
about that part,
but, uh...

08:48.067 --> 08:49.834
When do you think
I should make my move?

08:49.834 --> 08:52.868
You'll know when
the time is right.

08:52.868 --> 08:55.934
Man! I'm gonna
get me an old woman.

09:00.200 --> 09:01.801
What an idiot.

09:02.868 --> 09:06.234
"Odie, did you eat
my la-sag-knee?"

09:06.234 --> 09:08.534
