09:11.934 --> 09:13.534
Hi, Mrs. Rhoades.

09:14.834 --> 09:16.334
I guess you heard the news.

09:16.334 --> 09:18.968
Oh, you mean about how
Mr. Rhoades used and left you

09:18.968 --> 09:21.901
like you were the hand wipe
in the men's room
at the bus station?

09:23.033 --> 09:26.334
Ahem, yes.
That news.

09:26.334 --> 09:27.400
Straw head.

09:29.434 --> 09:31.200
Mrs. Rhoades,
let me help you out.

09:31.200 --> 09:33.400
See, you're a nerd girl.

09:35.901 --> 09:37.734
And nerd girls get dumped.

09:37.734 --> 09:39.901
It's as inevitable as
death in Texas.

09:42.767 --> 09:45.934
So, what you've gotta do
is get yourself a new guy.

09:45.934 --> 09:48.100
Oh, no more men for me.

09:48.100 --> 09:52.701
