together for so long.

11:11.534 --> 11:14.133
I understand.

11:14.133 --> 11:16.501
How could I
have been so blind?

11:16.501 --> 11:20.000
Look, uh, let's
cut through
the fancy talk.

11:20.000 --> 11:23.434
We both know what
we want here. Mm. Mm.

11:25.334 --> 11:26.634
[LOUD SLAP]

11:30.501 --> 11:33.534
And if you ever
touch me again,

11:33.534 --> 11:37.634
I will slap you so hard,
even your name
will be swollen.

11:39.000 --> 11:40.000
Got me?

11:40.000 --> 11:41.000
[SQUEALING]
Uh-huh.

11:50.968 --> 11:52.634
What did I
do wrong?

11:52.634 --> 11:54.133
Nothing.

11:54.133 --> 11:56.267
Don't you know
anything about women?

11:56.267 --> 11:59.701
Well, no.

11:59.701 --> 12:01.133
