"Yes, yes," in her eyes.

12:06.734 --> 12:08.634
Really?

12:08.634 --> 12:10.267
Sure. Listen,

12:10.267 --> 12:13.033
next time she bends over,
you just take...

12:16.067 --> 12:17.267
Hi, Marcie.

12:17.267 --> 12:19.367
