12:51.701 --> 12:54.734
You can't tell me you've
never fantasized about that.

12:56.601 --> 13:00.334
Come on, Marcie.
We all have.

13:01.367 --> 13:03.234
[LAUGHTER]

13:03.234 --> 13:04.968
See?

13:04.968 --> 13:08.167
Now, what you've got to do
is start thinking
about yourself.

13:08.167 --> 13:10.133
Be selfish.

13:10.133 --> 13:13.601
I know. Take us
on a vacation. Huh.

13:15.267 --> 13:17.767
That'll show
that damn Al.

13:17.767 --> 13:19.334
I-- I mean,
Steve.

13:20.734 --> 13:23.100
A vacation.
God, I wish I could.

13:23.100 --> 13:24.834
