get the money?

13:24.834 --> 13:28.801
Gee...that's a tough one
when you don't have kids
to steal from.

13:30.634 --> 13:32.868
I know. Sell something
of Steve's.

13:32.868 --> 13:35.267
He took everything...
except his stereo.

13:35.267 --> 13:37.767
And he wants me to
crate it and ship it to him.

13:37.767 --> 13:39.767
I guess you can't be
a real park ranger

13:39.767 --> 13:43.634
<i>without the theme
from Brigadoon
blasting on your stereo.</i>

13:43.634 --> 13:45.734
Sell it.

13:45.734 --> 13:46.934
I tell you what.

13:46.934 --> 13:48.334
Would it make you
feel better

13:48.334 --> 13:51.467
