and came with you?

13:51.467 --> 13:52.868
Oh, Peggy, would you?

13:52.868 --> 13:53.868
AL:
Hey, Peg!

13:53.868 --> 13:56.634
Come pop this thing
under my arm!

13:59.367 --> 14:01.200
Well, let's go first thing
in the morning.

14:01.200 --> 14:03.901
Al's a tiger after
he's been popped.

14:09.501 --> 14:12.434
I don't know, Kel.
I did everything
you said.

14:13.501 --> 14:15.400
I goosed her.
I blew in her ear.

14:16.734 --> 14:19.167
I even made
that sexy sound
with my armpit.

14:21.534 --> 14:22.601
