frigid?

14:24.234 --> 14:26.834
You know, Bud,
it's time to
step things up.

14:26.834 --> 14:29.067
You've got to show her
that you're for real.

14:29.067 --> 14:31.934
Do something
that screams romance.

14:31.934 --> 14:34.767
Buy a single rose, hold it
in between your teeth

14:34.767 --> 14:35.934
and wait for her
in her bed.

14:37.701 --> 14:40.200
