15:23.400 --> 15:25.534
Las Vegas!

15:27.968 --> 15:29.734
Woah!

15:31.100 --> 15:33.701
Oh! The lights,
the money.

15:33.701 --> 15:35.133
The men!

15:35.133 --> 15:37.400
I'm as giddy
as a widow.

15:37.400 --> 15:40.467
Well...let's just
check in.

15:40.467 --> 15:43.234
After a nice bubble bath
and a good night's sleep,

15:43.234 --> 15:44.801
