and early.

15:44.801 --> 15:47.934
I hear they've got
a really neat dam
not far from here.

15:47.934 --> 15:50.234
Oh, it's gonna be
so much-- Peggy?

15:50.234 --> 15:52.000
Come on, baby.

15:52.000 --> 15:53.801
Mama needs
a new pair of men.

15:55.934 --> 15:57.801
[COINS CLATTER]

15:57.801 --> 16:00.467
I won! I won!

16:00.467 --> 16:03.534
