stay in business?

16:05.434 --> 16:06.801
Let me play!
Let me play!

16:06.801 --> 16:07.801
ALL:
Yay!

16:08.901 --> 16:11.133
Oh. what are we messing
with quarters for?

16:11.133 --> 16:12.501
The real money's
over there.

16:12.501 --> 16:13.701
Come on, Marcie,
let's go.

16:13.701 --> 16:15.133
Oh. Maybe we should
take it slow.

16:15.133 --> 16:16.868
Not when we're
on a streak.

16:16.868 --> 16:19.267
We just got here and
we're almost up a buck.

16:20.567 --> 16:21.567
We're hot.

16:21.567 --> 16:22.901
Come on, grab the bags.

16:23.934 --> 16:24.934
Excuse me.

16:24.934 --> 16:26.868
Excuse me.
Make way. Make way.

16:26.868 --> 16:27.968
Ho-ho-ho-ho.

16:27.968 --> 16:29.567
Excuse me.
Make way. Make way.

16:30.701 --> 16:32.400
Oh! Don't you
recognize

16:32.400 --> 16:34.767
