you see one? Ha-ha.

16:37.367 --> 16:38.601
[COINS CLATTER]

16:39.868 --> 16:41.400
[LAUGHS]

16:44.767 --> 16:48.534
God. What did they have,
a toupee sale here?

16:57.434 --> 16:59.934
I would like
$20 worth of chips

16:59.934 --> 17:03.801
