Give me room.

17:14.367 --> 17:17.133
Oh, not you.
You stay close.

17:18.434 --> 17:19.733
Let's go!

17:26.534 --> 17:29.100
Lady...roll them
or buy them.

17:29.100 --> 17:31.000
