17:31.000 --> 17:34.901
C'mon baby.
Give me a seven
or send me to heaven.

17:35.767 --> 17:36.767
Seven.

17:36.767 --> 17:37.901
[CROWD CHEERING]

17:37.901 --> 17:38.901
Did we win?

17:38.901 --> 17:41.100
Of course we won.

17:41.100 --> 17:44.100
You know what they say:
bad marriage, good luck.

17:44.100 --> 17:45.334
Place your bets.

17:45.334 --> 17:46.634
Okay.

17:46.634 --> 17:49.767
Don't give me a two
because my husband
sells shoes.

17:50.801 --> 17:51.801
Seven.

17:51.801 --> 17:53.033
[CROWD CHEERING]
Aah!

17:53.033 --> 17:55.701
Oh! We won again!
We won again!

17:55.701 --> 17:57.501
How does this place
stay in business?

17:57.501 --> 18:00.868
Oh, I don't know, Marce...
but grease up the men
and shoot the women,

18:00.868 --> 18:02.667
because I'm a-rolling!

18:06.868 --> 18:08.501
Well, what are we
gonna do now?

18:08.501 --> 18:11.467
