tickets home.

18:15.334 --> 18:18.367
And we can't even
afford a room.

18:18.367 --> 18:19.501
Yeah...

18:19.501 --> 18:21.767
but we had fun,
didn't we?

18:21.767 --> 18:23.767
Yeah. Yeah, right.

18:23.767 --> 18:26.567
Well, I guess I'll go
fluff up a cactus
and sleep in the desert.

18:26.567 --> 18:27.901
Well, you know
what they say:

18:27.901 --> 18:29.868
the early bird catches
the Gila monster.
Hm.

18:31.067 --> 18:34.567
Boy, you lose your husband
and your life savings.

18:34.567 --> 18:36.701
It doesn't take much
to bring you down,
does it?

18:36.701 --> 18:37.801
[LAUGHS]

18:39.601 --> 18:41.534
You know, I just know
if I had a bigger stake,

18:41.534 --> 18:43.601
I could break this place.

18:43.601 --> 18:46.300
There's just got to be
a way to get more money.

18:46.300 --> 18:47.501
[SIGHS]

18:57.834 --> 19:00.934
Hello, Sergeant?
This is Al Bundy again.

19:00.934 --> 19:04.067
Listen, I'm...really starting
to get worried now.

19:05.400 --> 19:07.300
I'm sorry. It's getting hard
for me to talk.

19:07.300 --> 19:09.100
Let me...calm down.

19:09.100 --> 19:10.801
A description?

19:10.801 --> 19:12.667
Okay.

19:12.667 --> 19:14.634
Nineteen inch, diagonal.

19:20.234 --> 19:22.167
Has a...maple--

19:23.300 --> 19:24.801
Maple console.

19:24.801 --> 19:26.667
And it's got notches in it
from where the--

19:26.667 --> 19:28.267
Where the kids grew.

19:28.267 --> 19:29.634
[CRIES]

19:30.868 --> 19:32.200
Dad, what about Mom?

19:32.200 --> 19:34.667
Oh, yeah, my wife's
missing too. Uh...

19:35.634 --> 19:36.934
What? A description?

19:36.934 --> 19:39.033
I don't know.
Listen...you guys
are awful busy.

19:39.033 --> 19:40.400
Why don't you find
the TV first,

19:40.400 --> 19:42.067
and then we'll worry
about the wife.

19:42.067 --> 19:43.234
Yeah.

19:43.234 --> 19:45.834
Uh, listen, let me know
if you hear anything, huh?

19:45.834 --> 19:47.000
All right. Goodbye.

19:58.000 --> 20:02.767
Why didn't I let you know
how I felt about you
when I had the chance?

20:02.767 --> 20:05.367
Gee, Dad, we've never
seen you touched
like this before.

20:05.367 --> 20:08.701
Well, it's just that
I loved that TV so much.

20:08.701 --> 20:11.267
We all did, Dad.
Yeah.

20:11.267 --> 20:13.067
[DOORBELL RINGS]

20:13.067 --> 20:14.067
Who is it?

20:14.067 --> 20:15.367
Pizza
boy.

20:21.334 --> 20:22.367
Here.

20:22.367 --> 20:23.501
Twelve dollars,
please.

20:23.501 --> 20:24.501
Yep.

20:24.501 --> 20:25.634
[LAUGHS]

20:25.634 --> 20:27.501
No, Mr. Bundy,
I'm gonna need cash.

20:27.501 --> 20:29.801
Uh, your credit card
was rejected.

20:29.801 --> 20:32.467
What? That's impossible.
I just paid it off.

20:32.467 --> 20:33.667
[SIGHS]

20:33.667 --> 20:36.701
Look, Bundy, I held up
my part of the deal.

20:36.701 --> 20:40.133
I sideswiped a hearse
to get you this pizza
in 22 minutes.

20:40.133 --> 20:42.100
Fork over
the 12 bucks.

20:42.100 --> 20:44.267
I don't have
that kind of money.

20:55.834 --> 20:58.033
Wait a second.
I'll take care
of this.

20:58.033 --> 20:59.968
I know my credit's
good.

21:06.033 --> 21:07.367
Hello. Al Bundy here.

21:08.734 --> 21:11.200
Yes, "No Tip" Bundy.

21:11.200 --> 21:14.534
Now, look, it seems you people
made a little mistake.

21:14.534 --> 21:17.100
Now, I ordered a pizza
and it seems my credit card
was-- What?

21:18.634 --> 21:22.467
No, I did not charge $5000
in the last 10 minutes.

21:25.834 --> 21:27.767
I see.

21:27.767 --> 21:31.133
And just exactly where did my
wife spend this alleged 5 grand?

21:33.200 --> 21:34.467
Thank you very much.

21:37.634 --> 21:41.133
Kids, get a change of clothes
and a baseball bat...

21:41.133 --> 21:42.934
because we're going to Vegas!

